node.text:
Komunitas merupakan salah satu public figure, dimana didalam segala kegiatannya pasti akan disorot oleh berbagai mata masyarakat. Ibarat pepatah, akibat nila setitik rusak susu sebelanga.

Maka dari itu kami @idsilverians berkomitmen untuk selalu menjadi komunitas pelopor keselamatan berkendara. Safety Talk merupakan agenda rutin dalam setiap kegiatan kopdar. Tidak semata hanya kumpul semata. Bahkan dalam masa pandemik saat ini menjadi kebiasaan baru melalui media virtual kami kerap mealakukan coaching2 safety yang mana membahas segala dinamika kendaran dan pola pikir berkendara yang aman.

Bicara mengemudi kita tidak hanya bisa mengadandalkan keterampilan maupun pengalaman, karena hal tsb hanya sebatas membawa kita dalam aktifitas mengemudinya. Namun bicara safety/keselamatan, pola pikir (mindset-lah) yg utama, dimana kita harus dapat memahami potensi segala resiko berada dijalan raya dengan pergerakan yg sangat dinamisnya dari pengguna jalan lain.

Layaknya berada di medan perang, strategi adalah kunci utama. Maka kami sebagai komunitas sangat berperan untuk menjadi kepanjangan tangan dari instansi terkait demi terciptanya keselamatan berlalu lintas, tidak hanya belajar tentang defensive driving dari berbagai narasumber namun jg mempraktekan dalam keseharian kami mengemudi.

Tak hanya itu, kegiatan kopdar bersih2 kabin pun juga dilakukan yaitu dgn cara melakukan fogging. Dan tetap menerapkan protokol keamanan dengan memakai masker.

node.text: Good morning Di, I'm glad you rescued your hydrangeas, ? very pretty.  Good to see Andrew thriving too, that's very special ? Im sure you will all have a great BBQ and lots of fun and I'm sending good vibes for sunshine and no rain (or wind)! Have a fab day ??
Beautiful colour l brought some in too, mine are going brown from the sun!! I got them hanging hoping the will dry for autumn but am never very good at it! ??
Ooh, well done with 'Andrew' hope he continues to grow and thrive for you ?? I'll cross everything for you rain wise this afternoon, but enjoy anyway ?? xx
Those look so good in the tin , gave a lovely  bbq
Awwwww!!! Look at Andrew bless him!! ???
How lovely, what a very special olive tree. Enjoy your BBQ!.?xxx
I'm hoping Sept will be lovely

I'm hoping Sept will be lovely

I had to rescue these hydrangeas yesterday as they were being battered by the wind and rain. Summer seems to be over but I’m still hopeful for a sunny September once the schools go back. (Ever the optimist!) Also in this shot is ‘Andrew’ my little olive tree grown from an olive brought back from Bethlehem for me by little sis @mariajackson12z.  I’m pleased to report that after a 5 month hibernation he’s now got 17 leaves and is strong and healthy.  I’m so impressed!! 
I also cleaned the windows yesterday for today’s birthday barbecue.  It looks like being a soggy one .. 
happy Saturday lovelies ?

#Namaste ?
French president Emmanuel Macron leaned forward and folded his hands in the traditional Indian "namaste" as he welcomed German Chancellor Angela Merkel at his Mediterranean holiday retreat, the Fort of Bregancon, in southern France.
The German Chancellor reciprocated with what is becoming a popular form of greeting among world leaders in the time of the coronavirus pandemic. 
The two leaders are meeting at the French President's summer residence to discuss a long list of subjects including the pandemic, post-election unrest in Belarus and growing tensions with Turkey.

node.text:
How can we create intimacy in a digital world?
In her final project, @noail examines how human contact, which is an existential and important need for physical and mental health, can be mediated in the new reality of the Covid-19 epidemic and the rules of social distance.

By mapping the existing types of touch and creating an interactive touch dictionary that categorizes and categorizes them into different categories, Noa tried to understand one of the basic components of interpersonal communication, which was obvious to us and suddenly became the most missing, distant and precious thing to us.
Inspired by the dictionary, Ilan has created a series of objects displayed in a store that invites visitors to explore and experience new types of touch and explore them as new components in interpersonal communication.

Noa Ilan is a partner in interior design at NM Design Studio, a ceramicist and illustrator from Tel Aviv. Ilan holds a bachelor's degree in interior design from the Holon Institute of Technology and a recent graduate of the  #aboutdesign track.
*

Voters will be provided with gloves to press the EVM button and COVID-19 patients in quarantine will be allowed to vote at the last hour of the polling day, according to broad guidelines issued by the Election Commission on Friday for holding elections during the coronavirus pandemic.

The gloves will most likely be disposable. A separate set of guidelines will be issued for voters who are residing in areas notified as “containment zone”, the Election Commission said.

According to a report by Indian Express, the Election Commission had asked political parties to contribute suggestions which would go towards forming the guidelines.

The release of this set of guidelines signals that the Bihar state assembly polls are likely to be held, becoming the first to be conducted in the country amid the pandemic. The polls are likely to be held sometime in October-November.

The demand to defer the assembly elections in Bihar had been quite loud, with National Democratic Alliance (NDA) partner, Lok Janshakti Party (LJP) joining the Rashtriya Janata Dal (RJD) and Congress in clamouring for the polls to be postponed in the face of a steady rise in the cases of COVID-19 in the state.

‘Boaty McBoatface’ plays a starring role in the Science Museum’s free exhibition ‘Driverless: who's in control?’ ?  A little history for any followers who aren’t aware of this tragic victim of a broken democratic system: In 2016, The Natural Environment Research Council in Britain created a public ‘Name Our Ship’ online poll for a £200m polar research ship ? The funding council asked for submissions that were “inspirational and about environmental and polar science”; dignified names like Endeavour, Shackleton and Falcon were among those suggested ?? However, the Internet can rarely be trusted to take things seriously and when the poll opened, the joke name ‘Boaty McBoatface’ shot to the top of the list.  The website was overwhelmed and crashed.  By the time the poll closed, Boaty McBoatface had nearly 30,000 votes (almost 10 x as many as the second popular choice, the RRS Henry Worsley).
Heartbreakingly, the public vote was eventually overruled and the ship was named ‘RRS Sir David Attenborough’ instead.  An onboard submersible (shown here) was awarded the name as a compromise? However, a faith-restoring turn of events followed: Swedish rail company MTR Express and newspaper Metro jointly held a public vote to name a train running between Stockholm and Gothenburg.  The result? ‘Trainy McTrainface’ ?? (see slide 2!) MTR said the Boaty McBoatface decision had caused disappointment worldwide and it hoped the name Trainy McTrainface would “be received with joy by many, not only in Sweden.” ??

node.text:
Ikan Marlin Steak?
Ikan Marlin memiliki banyak manfaat untuk kesehatan tubuh manusia, karena ikan marlin mengandung banyak nutrisi yang baik. Gizi di dalam Marlin Putih lebih banyak, jika dibanding dengan gizi pada sumber makanan hewani lainnya, misalnya pada daging.

manfaat ikan marlinbagi kesehatan, antara lain:
1. Mengandung vitamin A
Dengan mengonsumsi ikan marlin maka kita juga akan mendapatkan manfaat kandungan vitamin A bagi penglihatan yang baik dan kondisi mata yang sehat. 
2. Mengandung vitamin D
Vitamin D sangat penting untuk menjaga kesehatan tulang dan gigi manusia, daging ikan marlin bisa memenuhi kebutuhan kalsium, fosfor dan vitamin D sekaligus untuk tubuh manusia.
3. Mengandung kalsium
Setiap orang memiliki kebutuhan kalsium yang berbeda, Kalsium dari daging ikan marlin juga berfungsi sebagai pembakar lemak sehingga baik untuk diet tinggi kalsium yang dapat mengoptimalkan pengeluaran lemak dan menekan nafsu makan.
4. Mengandung omega 3
Asam lemak omega 3 bisa membantu meningkatkan pertumbuhan sel otak janin, bayi dan balita, meningkatkan sistem kekebalan tubuh dan menghindarkan serangan penyakit.
5. Mengandung vitamin B kompleks
Kandungan tersebut akan membuat rambut tidak mudah kusam dan rontok sehingga kondisi kulit kepala pun berada dalam keadaan yang sehat. 
6. Mengontrol aliran darah
Ikan marlin biru yang mengandung polisakarida yang dapat bermanfaat untuk mengontrol aliran darah sehingga terhindar dari masalah penyumbatan.
7. Mengandung zat besi
Kandungan zat besi dalam ikan Marlin lebih mudah diserap tubuh daripada sumber zat besi lainnya seperti serealia atau kacang – kacangan. 

Besarnya manfaat ikan marlin membuat jenis ikan ini menjadi layak dikonsumsi untuk memenuhi ketuhanan vitamin sobat semua. Dapurku menyediakan berbagai jenis ikan lainnya juga lho.

node.text: I’ve become obsessed with my bedroom view ~ actually the beautiful 82 year priest... Some days there are four funerals in a row {with coffins of all sizes and expense}. He stays back at night to counsel the bereft, opens the doors day after day for the next grieving family. He holds himself with the same poise daily, he is unfailingly respectful ~ almost makes me want to be a priest ?. Most people attending are not allowed into the church (#socialdistancing ), so they lean on my fence and cry behind their masks. I have started to occasionally talk to the mourners ~ the Greek elderly have told me that many of the deaths have been due to COVID-19.... The nursing homes and the numbers, that seem so distant or unknown, is daily dealt with by this community and priest #massisolationaus #australialockeddown #ballaratfoto #auswip #documentaryphotography #24hourproject_alonetogether #bedroomwindowview #massisolationformat #shotoniphone #priest #greekorthodoxchurch #womenphotographerscommunity #brunswick #artquarantined
